# Cursor Rules (repo-level)
#
# Goal: make Cursor's AI-generated git commit messages follow a consistent
# Chinese "summary + details" format (Conventional Commits).
#
# If you use Cursor's "Generate Commit Message", output MUST be:
# <type>: <中文概述>
#
# <中文详情（1-4 行，说明改了什么/为什么）>
# 修改了 N 个文件。
#
# Constraints:
# - Plain text only (no markdown / bullets / code fences)
# - type ∈ feat|fix|refactor|perf|docs|test|chore
# - "修改了 N 个文件。" only when N is known; do not guess


